  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Word has it that you’ve become a fine blacksmith. I want to see for myself if the rumors are true. Judging by your tools and your stance, it seems you’ve built up quite a bit of skill and experience. Care to show me what you can do?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Confident, aren’t you? Good! Then go defeat #r#o20#s and #o21#s#k, and bring #ban #t4010105# and a #t4010106##k. You can find #o20# around #m10004000#, and #o21# appears to be in the Ant Tunnel in #m10005000#. Shouldn’t be too difficult. I’ll be waiting!"
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Looks like you haven’t quite reached that level of skill, have you?"
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Let’s see… these are exceptionally well made. I’m genuinely impressed that you’ve reached this level of craftsmanship. Yes, this is the quality one would expect from a true blacksmith. Your dedication to honing your skills is admirable. I suppose this calls for a special reward."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "This #t4130000# is a unique item that can alter the abilities of equipment when used during crafting. Because it’s so delicate, you may sometimes get disappointing results, but if handled properly, it might produce something far beyond your expectations."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "If you want to test the limits of your blacksmithing skills, I highly recommend giving it a try. Keep striving forward!"
        }
      },
